(iv)  using  the  abbreviation  “C.Tech.”  for  Certified 
Technician  and  his  specialisation  after  his  name 
with the approval of the Board;

(e)   if  his  qualification  has  been  withdrawn  or  cancelled  by 
the authority through which it was acquired or by which 
it was awarded;

(i)   if he is found by the Board to have contravened or failed 
to  comply  with  this  Act  or  any  regulations  made  under 
this Act;

